When implementing a new investment strategy, seek guidance from someone experienced in that particular strategy.
 
Hameto Benkreira, Head of Growth Product at PadSplit, shares his advice on seeking guidance for new investment strategies. He emphasizes that this guidance can save your company from serious risks
